                <div class="block-content">
      <p>WFNS fosters creative writing and the profession of writing in the Province of Nova Scotia; provides advice and assistance to writers at all stages of their careers; encourages greater public recognition of Nova Scotian writers and their achievements; and enhances the literary arts in our regional and national culture.</p><p><a href="/about-membership.html">LEARN ABOUT MEMBERSHIP</a> <a href="/about-membership/become-member.html">BECOME A MEMBER</a> <a class="last" href="/about-membership/renew-your-membership.html">RENEW YOUR MEMBERSHIP</a></p>    </div>
