  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <span class="field-content"><a href="/blog/discounted-membership-begins-august-1.html-0">Discounted membership begins August 1</a></span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-created">        <span class="field-content">Thursday, July 7, 2016 - 12:15pm</span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>If you're a lapsed or new member, you can join the WFNS for $30 for the balance of 2016! Membership is valid from August 1 - December 31, 2016. If you register prior to August 1, you will be activated just after that date.</p>
<p>Membership entitles you to a bi-weekly member email, a digital subscription to <em>Eastword</em>, discounts on programming, and more! </p>
<p><a href="http://writers.ns.ca/about-membership/become-member.html">Click here for information on membership! </a></p>
