  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <span class="field-content"><a href="/blog/2016-east-coast-literary-awards-shortlist-announced.html">2016 East Coast Literary Awards Shortlist Announced </a></span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-created">        <span class="field-content">Wednesday, May 4, 2016 - 3:53pm</span>  </div>  
  



  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Halifax, NS – The Writers’ Federation of Nova Scotia (WFNS) is proud to announce the shortlist for the 2016 East Coast Literary Awards. These three Awards celebrate the quality and diversity of writing in non-fiction, poetry, and fiction by Atlantic Canadian writers. The shortlisted writers for each Award are:</p>
<p><strong>Evelyn Richardson Non-Fiction Award:<br /></strong>Dean Jobb (NS), <em>Empire of Deception</em> (HarperCollins)<br />Marq de Villiers (NS),<em> Back to the Well</em> (Goose Lane)<br />Gary L. Saunders (NS), <em>My Life With Trees</em> (Gaspereau Press)</p></div>  </div>  
  



  
